quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  38,84,"(Allah) daali: "Mi wooɗndirii goonga, ko goonga mi wowlata,"
  38,85,"ma Mi hebbinire Jahannama, e ɓen jokkuɓe ma fof e maɓɓe"."
  38,86,"Maaku: "Mi laɓndaaki on njoɓdi e fii ɗum; mi wonaali jeyaaɗo e sincooɓe(deftatoobe)."
  38,87,"Ndee [Alqur’aanaare] wonaani, si wonaa waaju tageefo ngon."
  38,88,"Ma on nganndu (fii) kabaaru mayre, ko neeɓaa !"."
  39,1,"Jippagol deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, pooluɗo, ñeeño oon."
  39,2,"Min njippiniirii deftere nden e maaɗa, e hoore goonga. rewu allah, laɓɓinanaa mo diina ka."
  39,3,"Ngaanndee, ko Allah woodani diina laaɓuka kan. Ɓeen non ɓe ɓeya nogitori yiɗɓe ga makko (hara hiɓe wi'a): "Min ngaalaa rewirde ɗi, si wonaa tun no ɗi ɓannira min ka Allah, ɓadal". Pellet, Allah Ñaawoyat hakkunde maɓɓe, e kon ko ɓe woni lurrude e mun. Pellet, Allah feewnata on gonɗo fewnoowo, ɗuuɗuɗo jeddugol."
  39,4,"Sinno Allah yiɗno, nde o siforta ɓiɗɗo, O suɓayno ko o yiɗi woo, e ko o tagi kon. Senaare woodanii mo ! Ko Kaŋko woni Allah, Bajjo, pooluɗo on."
  39,5,"O tagirii kammuuji ɗiin e leydi ndin, goonga.Homo suddira jemma on ñalaema oon, O suddira ñalawma on jemma on. O eelti na'ange ngen e lewru ndun, kala majji no doga haa e lajal taƴaangal. Nganndee, ko Kaŋko woni pooluɗo, kaforoowo On."